article.description: — Jao Ituka had 20 points as Marist topped Niagara 77-70 on Monday night.
article.headline: Ituka scores 20 to guide Marist past Niagara 77-70
article.linkText: Ituka scores 20 to guide Marist past Niagara 77-70
article.story: POUGHKEEPSIE, N.Y. -- — Jao Ituka had 20 points as Marist topped Niagara 77-70 on Monday night. Ricardo Wright had 19 points and six rebounds for the Red Foxes (11-13, 6-9 Metro Atlantic Athletic Conference). Jordan Jones added 18 points and three blocks. Marcus Hammond had 21 points and six rebounds for the Purple Eagles (11-13, 6-9). Julian Mackey added 16 points. Noah Thomasson had 13 points and six rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ Portions of this story were generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
